296
01:11:15,733 --> 01:11:16,566
<b>Possibly true.</b>

297
01:11:16,966 --> 01:11:18,466
<b>Military governments manipulate</b>

298
01:11:18,466 --> 01:11:20,666
<b>anti-French sentiment for legitimacy.</b>

299
01:11:21,433 --> 01:11:22,366
<b>Definitely true.</b>

300
01:11:23,033 --> 01:11:24,233
<b>Both points matter.</b>

301
01:11:24,766 --> 01:11:26,066
<b>But neither addresses</b>

302
01:11:26,066 --> 01:11:27,433
<b>the fundamental question.</b>

303
01:11:28,333 --> 01:11:30,633
<b>Why do policies designed to help</b>

304
