312
01:11:49,166 --> 01:11:50,733
<b>Here's what makes it systematic.</b>

313
01:11:51,600 --> 01:11:52,766
<b>Operation Persil</b>

314
01:11:52,766 --> 01:11:54,566
<b>wasn't one bad decision.</b>

315
01:11:54,899 --> 01:11:57,833
<b>In 1958, the CFA franc</b>

316
01:11:57,833 --> 01:11:59,866
<b>arrangements continue today.</b>

317
01:12:00,466 --> 01:12:03,333
<b>Military interventions from the 1960s</b>

318
