<b>through 2023 followed similar patterns.</b>

319
01:12:07,466 --> 01:12:10,733
<b>When policies fail for 60 years across</b>

320
01:12:10,733 --> 01:12:13,733
<b>multiple countries, that's not accident.</b>

321
01:12:14,133 --> 01:12:16,366
<b>The Sahel crisis isn't an anomaly</b>

322
01:12:16,366 --> 01:12:18,399
<b>requiring external management.</b>

323
01:12:19,100 --> 01:12:21,266
<b>It's the outcome of relationships never</b>

324
01:12:21,266 --> 01:12:22,566
