01:12:22,566 --> 01:12:24,300
<b>genuine sovereignty or</b>

326
01:12:24,333 --> 01:12:25,833
<b>self-sustaining development.</b>

327
01:12:26,566 --> 01:12:28,533
<b>Whether these new military governments</b>

328
01:12:28,533 --> 01:12:29,566
