333
01:12:40,833 --> 01:12:42,800
<b>But the pattern of resistance itself</b>

334
01:12:42,800 --> 01:12:44,666
<b>reveals something important.</b>

335
01:12:45,533 --> 01:12:47,633
<b>The relationship between France and its</b>

336
01:12:47,633 --> 01:12:49,933
