338
01:12:51,466 --> 01:12:53,033
<b>military force and</b>

339
01:12:53,033 --> 01:12:55,000
<b>economic leverage can't resolve.</b>

340
01:12:55,633 --> 01:12:57,133
<b>The question isn't whether these</b>

341
01:12:57,133 --> 01:12:59,366
<b>particular coup leaders deserve support.</b>

342
01:13:00,133 --> 01:13:02,000
<b>It's whether we'll analyze African</b>

343
01:13:02,000 --> 01:13:03,933
<b>politics through myths</b>

344
01:13:03,933 --> 01:13:06,033
<b>that serve external interests,</b>

345
