346
01:13:08,899 --> 01:13:10,133
<b>patterns that drive</b>

347
01:13:10,133 --> 01:13:11,933
<b>genuine political change.</b>

348
01:13:12,433 --> 01:13:14,266
<b>Even when that change looks messy and</b>

349
01:13:14,266 --> 01:13:16,233
<b>uncertain, because the</b>

350
01:13:16,233 --> 01:13:18,166
<b>coup belt isn't random chaos.</b>

351
01:13:18,800 --> 01:13:20,933
<b>It's the geography where post-colonial</b>

352
01:13:20,933 --> 01:13:23,133
<b>arrangements are being rejected.</b>

